Simple quote bot with isaac
===========================

This is just a simple bot i wrote to have fun with my colleagues in IRC to keep
track of the most significant quotations

Commands
--------

#### Channel commands
* !quote -- take a random quote from the database
* !quote *<string>* -- take a random quotation from database that contain _string_
* !quote add <quote> -- save the _quote_ in the database

* !op -- gives op to users from op table
* !op add <username> -- adds username to op table of calling user is in it

#### Private message commands
* !join <channel> -- Request to join _channel_ to the bot

